OL,3,CDad-of-three who pushed riot officer
OL,4,Cto ground jailed
OL,6,FA father-of-three who was the
OL,7,F"catalyst" for an attack on a police
OL,8,Fofficer by pushing him to the ground
OL,9,Fduring rioting in Rotherham has been
OL,10,Fjailed.
OL,12,FRichard Harrison was caught on body-
OL,13,Fworn camera shoving the officer, who
OL,14,Fwas holding a riot shield outside a
OL,15,Fhotel housing hundreds of asylum
OL,16,Fseekers, on 4 August.
