OL,3,CDad-of-three who pushed riot officer
OL,4,Cto ground jailed
OL,6,FThe 37-year-old, of Ings Field Lane,
OL,7,FWath-Upon-Dearne, was one of hundreds
OL,8,Fof people who gathered outside the
OL,9,FHoliday Inn Express for an anti-
OL,10,Fimmigration protest.
OL,12,FIn violent scenes, police were
OL,13,Fattacked and the hotel's windows were
OL,14,Fsmashed. A group of rioters got into
OL,15,Fthe hotel and a bin was pushed against
OL,16,Fthe building and set alight.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
