OL,3,CDad-of-three who pushed riot officer
OL,4,Cto ground jailed
OL,6,FProsecutor Neil Coxon told Sheffield
OL,7,FCrown Court Harrison's push was the
OL,8,F"catalyst" for the officer being
OL,9,Fassaulted by others in the crowd,
OL,10,Fincluding being punched and assaulted
OL,11,Fwith some kind of weapon.
OL,13,FThe court was shown multiple video
OL,14,Fclips of him at different stages in
OL,15,Fthe disorder, abusing police officers
OL,16,Fas they stood behind their shields.
OL,18,FBianca Brasoveanu, defending, said her
OL,19,Fclient was "shamed" by what he had
OL,20,Fdone and added that "drink is a demon
OL,21,Fhe's been battling all his life".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
