OL,3,CDad-of-three who pushed riot officer
OL,4,Cto ground jailed
OL,6,FHarrison, who had admitted violent
OL,7,Fdisorder at a previous hearing, was
OL,8,Fjailed for two years and six months.
OL,10,FAlso sentenced was Kurt Hooley, 34.
OL,12,FThe father-of-two tried to grab a
OL,13,Fpolice riot shield as he took part in
OL,14,Fthe violence in Rotherham.
OL,16,FJudge Sarah Wright heard Hooley was
OL,17,Fpart of a group throwing missiles at
OL,18,Fthe line of officers and screaming
OL,19,Fabuse at them, although there was no
OL,20,Fevidence he threw anything himself.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
