OL,3,CDad-of-three who pushed riot officer
OL,4,Cto ground jailed
OL,6,FJudge Wright said she had read a
OL,7,Fstatement from the female officer who
OL,8,Fwas targeted by Hooley, in which she
OL,9,Fsaid: "I cannot describe or put into
OL,10,Fwords how this incident has made me
OL,11,Ffeel."
OL,13,FThe judge said: "The fear and panic in
OL,14,Fthe officer's voice can clearly be
OL,15,Fheard in the footage."
OL,17,FThe court also heard a statement from
OL,18,Fa senior officer at the scene who
OL,19,Fsaid: "It felt like we were fighting
OL,20,Ffor our lives and the lives of the
OL,21,Fpeople in the hotel."
