OL,4,Cto ground jailed
OL,6,FThe officer said he believed those
OL,7,Fattacking the police deliberately
OL,8,Ftargeted smaller and female officers.
OL,10,FThe court heard Hooley's partner, who
OL,11,Fwas clearly upset in the public
OL,12,Fgallery, is expecting another child in
OL,13,FOctober.
OL,15,FThe defendant, who is of no fixed
OL,16,Fabode, admitted violent disorder at a
OL,17,Fprevious hearing.
OL,19,FJudge Wright told him it was a
OL,20,F"terrifying incident" and added "you
OL,21,Fwere at the fore".
